///
/// Registration
@node Registration
@{fg shine}@{b}Registration:@{par}
~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}@{par}

@{fg text}The "HSMathLibs" are Shareware. If you want to use the unrestricted version, you have to register first and pay the fee. Plaese
use the registerform on our homepage "http://WWW.HSMathLibs.de/" for registration. If you would like to get the full version via snail mail
just send me a disk (HD or DD) and an addressed envelope including postage or 3,- EUR (Euro) or 3,- $ (US Dollar) or 2,- Ł (UK Pound)
additional. You can find my address at @{" author " link Author}. Contact me for my Bankaccount.@{par}
When I have the money then I'll send you your registration number and login to download the full version and all updates from our Homepage.@{par}

@{b}price@{ub}@{par}
version for WinUAE:	5,- EUR (Euro) or 8,- $ (US Dollar) or 5,- Ł (UK Pound)@{par}
version for MC68881/82: 5,- EUR (Euro) or 8,- $ (US Dollar) or 5,- Ł (UK Pound)@{par}
version for MC68040:    5,- EUR (Euro) or 8,- $ (US Dollar) or 5,- Ł (UK Pound)@{par}
version for MC68060:    5,- EUR (Euro) or 8,- $ (US Dollar) or 5,- Ł (UK Pound)@{par}

@endnode
///
/// Copyright
@node Copyright
@{fg shine}@{b}Copyright:@{par}
~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}@{par}

@{fg text}The demo-version of "HSMathLibs" is freely distributable as long as it is NOT CHANGED and ALL files are included UNCHANGED.@{par}
@{b}The registered version of "HSMathLibs" is ONLY for registered users. "HSMathLibs" and the registration number MUST NOT be
published or copied@{ub}.@{par}

Re- or disassembling of "HSMathLibs" is NOT allowed.@{par}


@{b}@{i}@{u}MOST IMPORTANT:@{ub}@{ui}@{uu}@{par}

"HSMathLibs" is PROVIDED AS IS. Use it at your OWN RISK.@{par}

The author is NOT RESPONSIBLE for any data loss or damage caused directly or indirectly by the use of "HSMathLibs".@{par}

All rights reserved. Please send bug reports and suggestions.@{par}

@endnode
